PrecisAmendments to the ESQUIMALT GRAVING DOCK REGULATIONS, 1989 which update the rules so they reflect current methods of operation, address concerns respecting the qualifications of the dockmaster, the impact of operations on the environment and about safety during docking operations, as well as increase the fees for services provided at this fixed-foundation dry dock.
